cs.MM, cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.CV, cs.CR

The paper deals with the evaluation of multimedia delivery over HTTP Adaptive Streaming, which is a topic related to multimedia (cs.MM) and networked systems (cs.NI). The proposed model involves statistical analysis (cs.IT) and video quality assessment (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper discusses the potential impact of bandwidth fluctuations on the streaming quality, which is a security concern (cs.CR).
